task.summary:
Rooms exiting from are now responsible for moving the player's location.
Why didn't we change this sooner? I also alphabetically ordered the command list.
Made the player save the roomID (crucial!)
droppedItems now finally disappear when they realize they should not exist! Moving to a new room no longer goes to other rooms unexpectedly.
